subject: Any JUnit gurus in Hong Kong?
msgSnippet: If you are a JUnit guru (preferably developer) in Hong Kong, the Hong Kong Java User Group (http://www.hkjug.org/) would like to invite you to give a
messageBody:
If you are a JUnit guru (preferably developer) in Hong Kong, the Hong
Kong Java User Group (http://www.hkjug.org/) would like to invite you
to give a presentation about the JUnit project. If you're interested,
drop me a line at rmlowe-at-rmlowe-dot-com.

Best,

Robert Lowe
Program Director
The Hong Kong Java User Group
http://www.hkjug.org/
